data.description: Simply STUNNING home in the highly-desired area of Shady Acres! It is conveniently located near 610 North, I-10, The Washington Corridor, Memorial Park and The Galleria. This home boasts 10-ft ceilings, engineered hardwood floors, chandeliers, epoxy garage flooring, massive fans, spa like master bath AND a cozy backyard perfect for your morning coffee with privacy fence. Don't miss your opportunity to own this INCREDIBLE home! VA assumptions are welcome and lock in a rate that's under 5%! Parking won't be an issue with extra spaces inside the gated community. Empty lot across the street can be utilized as well for extra parking.
